344 Hicks Street, adjoining the northwest corner of Pacific Street. This is a brick house with a wooden colopade.
P. L. Sperr  January 1', 1941
Hicks St., B'klyn., from Pacific St. to Atlantic Ave.
Jan. 10, 1941
P. L. Sperr, photographer
